The Strongpin Vault is a cloud-based, secure and easy-to-use, password manager synchronized over your devices. Your vaults can be accessed through various applications, and this one is capable of automatically filling your credentials on websites.

This extension allows you to user your vaults with the highest possible security rating!
Features include:
* Create, read, updated and delete passwords stored inside your vaults;
* Automatically fill credentials on a website;
* Update/automatically create credentials upon login;
* Generate strong passwords;
* Organize your items using tags.

Opening a vault is performed by using the Ubiqu Authenticate app (REQUIRED, found here: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ubiqu.eid or https://itunes.apple.com/nl/app/authenticate/id934349819) as 2-Factor Authentication.
